{"story":{"group_1":[{"autoTurnFirst":4.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":403400,"motion":1,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_4034_00_01","textHome":"我担任学校的风纪委员。@因为要提醒学生，所以朋友们总是@说我“爱说教”……但又不是我想要说教的。@风纪乱了人心就乱，再说为了校园的秩序……@啊，对不起。我果然是有点爱说教？"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":7.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":403400}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.3,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_020.exp.json","id":403400,"motion":0}]},{"autoTurnFirst":5.3,"chara":[{"id":403400,"motion":200}]},{"autoTurnFirst":1.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp.json","id":403400,"motion":0}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":403400,"motion":100}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":403400}]}],"group_10":[{"autoTurnFirst":2.5,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":403400,"motion":200,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_4034_00_18","textHome":"之前的游泳比赛，我使出了自己最好的状态！@虽然和其他选手的成绩比起来……@下次新人战我一定会有更好的成绩的。哼哼！"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.0,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":403400}]},{"autoTurnFirst":7.0,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":403400,"motion":1}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.3,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":403400}]}],"group_11":[{"autoTurnFirst":1.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":403400,"motion":400,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_4034_00_19","textHome":"好！状态不错！我会牢牢记住这个感觉的！"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":1.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":403400}]},{"autoTurnFirst":1.8,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":1,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":403400,"motion":1}]},{"autoTurnFirst":0.1,"chara":[{"eyeClose":0,"id":403400}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.9,"chara":[{"id":403400}]}],"group_12":[{"autoTurnFirst":1.5,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":403400,"motion":200,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_4034_00_20","textHome":"哈啊……好爽！@感觉自己的脑袋一下子清醒起来了！"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.3,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":403400}]},{"autoTurnFirst":5.8,"chara":[{"id":403400,"motion":1}]}],"group_13":[{"autoTurnFirst":5.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_020.exp.json","id":403400,"motion":1,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_4034_00_21","textHome":"我……想要成为匡扶正义的存在。@我想拯救那些因为有人作恶而承受痛苦的人。"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":403400,"motion":300}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"eyeClose":1,"id":403400}]},{"autoTurnFirst":0.1,"chara":[{"eyeClose":0,"id":403400}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.9,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":403400,"motion":100}]}],"group_14":[{"autoTurnFirst":5.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":403400,"motion":300,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_4034_00_22","textHome":"其实，我有些害怕去消灭魔女。@但是靠着组队，大家都在身边让我放下心来。@在对抗魔女的时候，才会完全不害怕。@能一直四个人一起战斗就好了……开玩笑的！"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp.json","id":403400,"motion":0}]},{"autoTurnFirst":8.6,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":403400,"motion":1}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"eyeClose":1,"id":403400}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":403400,"motion":100}]}],"group_15":[{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp.json","id":403400,"motion":1,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_4034_00_23","textHome":"只要拥有力量，就能够改变现状吗？@不，没有力量也是能够做到的。@只要你想要改变的想法是认真的，@然后还有认同你想法的同伴陪着你……@无论何时，无论如何，现状都能得到改变。"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.9,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":403400,"motion":200}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.0,"chara":[{"eyeClose":1,"id":403400}]},{"autoTurnFirst":0.1,"chara":[{"eyeClose":0,"id":403400}]},{"autoTurnFirst":7.0,"chara":[{"id":403400,"motion":1}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":403400}]}],"group_16":[{"autoTurnFirst":2.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp.json","id":403400,"motion":1,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_4034_00_24","textHome":"来的好晚啊。你去做什么了啊？@好了，快点出发巡逻吧。@遥香前辈她们还在等着呢。"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":403400}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.6,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":403400,"motion":400}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":403400}]}],"group_17":[{"autoTurnFirst":1.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":403400,"motion":0,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_4034_00_25","textHome":"早上好！洗脸了吗？早饭吃了吗？@作业做完了吗？有没有东西落下？@嗯，好像没问题了。那就好！"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":403400,"motion":1}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.9,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":403400}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.2,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":403400,"motion":200}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":403400}]}],"group_18":[{"autoTurnFirst":2.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":403400,"motion":0,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_4034_00_26","textHome":"该是午餐时间了。@只不过，因为有像亚里纱这样的@在午饭前就偷吃便当的不规矩的家伙，@所以风纪委员在午饭前也不能疏忽大意。"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.7,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_020.exp.json","id":403400,"motion":1}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.2,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":403400}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.8,"chara":[{"id":403400,"motion":200}]}],"group_19":[{"autoTurnFirst":5.7,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":403400,"motion":1,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_4034_00_27","textHome":"我还要去游泳部练习，所以你先回去吧。@不过如果有兴趣的话，@你也可以来参观一下我的练习……@要来吗？"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.5,"chara":[{"id":403400,"motion":0}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp.json","id":403400,"motion":100}]}],"group_2":[{"autoTurnFirst":5.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":403400,"motion":200,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_4034_00_03","textHome":"哈啊……会变成什么样子呢……"}]}],"group_20":[{"autoTurnFirst":5.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":403400,"motion":200,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_4034_00_28","textHome":"明天我要和遥香前辈一起，做晨间问候工作。@因为要比平时起得早，所以差不多该睡了。"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":403400,"motion":0}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":403400,"motion":1}]}],"group_21":[{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_020.exp.json","id":403400,"motion":1,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_4034_00_29","textHome":"虽然他们是扰乱风纪的学生，@但是他们也有着各种各样复杂的缘由……@我也很理解这一点。"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":403400}]},{"autoTurnFirst":6.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":403400,"motion":300}]}],"group_22":[{"autoTurnFirst":3.3,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_020.exp.json","id":403400,"motion":200,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_4034_00_30","textHome":"最近有些事件发生……@所以我和大家说需要加强定期的巡逻。@那么！一起出发巡逻吧。"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.6,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":403400}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.3,"chara":[{"id":403400,"motion":400}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":403400}]}],"group_23":[{"autoTurnFirst":4.6,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":403400,"motion":300,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_4034_00_31","textHome":"真是……无法理解的地方。@诶！？诶诶，我才没有在害怕，放心啦。@这种时候，就应该冷静下来应对。"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":1.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp.json","id":403400,"motion":0}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.5,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"id":403400,"motion":400}]},{"autoTurnFirst":5.0,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_020.exp.json","id":403400,"motion":200}]}],"group_24":[{"autoTurnFirst":4.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp.json","id":403400,"motion":1,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_4034_00_32","textHome":"有这么多的魔法少女！？@啊啊，抱歉，这里不是应该退缩的时候。@我们也要振作精神上吧。"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":1.8,"chara":[{"id":403400,"motion":400}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.2,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":403400}]},{"autoTurnFirst":5.0,"chara":[{"id":403400,"motion":200}]}],"group_25":[{"autoTurnFirst":2.7,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":403400,"motion":300,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_4034_00_33","textHome":"在和遥香前辈组队之后，我发现了……@就算是一个人做不到的事，@只要有同伴帮忙就可以做到……"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.0,"chara":[{"eyeClose":1,"id":403400}]},{"autoTurnFirst":0.01,"chara":[{"eyeClose":0,"id":403400}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.0,"chara":[{"id":403400,"motion":0}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.0,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"id":403400,"motion":100}]}],"group_26":[{"autoTurnFirst":2.8,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":403400,"motion":1,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_4034_00_34","textHome":"因为亚里纱总是睡过头，@所以我早上就会去叫她起床。@让她生活变得有规律，@似乎是件很困难的事情……"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.9,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":403400}]},{"autoTurnFirst":6.8,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":403400,"motion":200}]}],"group_27":[{"autoTurnFirst":5.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp.json","id":403400,"motion":100,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_4034_00_35","textHome":"我说啊，你觉得我将来会做什么呢？@因为不会放过恶行，@所以会成为警察……或是法官之类的？"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":403400}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.5,"chara":[{"id":403400,"motion":1}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp.json","id":403400}]}],"group_28":[{"autoTurnFirst":3.5,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":403400,"motion":1,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_4034_00_36","textHome":"遥香前辈真的很厉害！@头脑很聪明，会随机应变，@又温柔体贴，大家都很依赖她……@也是我憧憬的存在。"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.8,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":403400}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":403400,"motion":0}]},{"autoTurnFirst":5.7,"chara":[{"eyeClose":1,"id":403400,"motion":300}]}],"group_29":[{"autoTurnFirst":7.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":403400,"motion":1,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_4034_00_37","textHome":"我和我的父亲相依为命。@我负责家务。诶？我并没有觉得很辛苦。@因为我喜欢做家务，爸爸也会来帮我！"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":1.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp.json","id":403400,"motion":0}]},{"autoTurnFirst":5.1,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":403400,"motion":100}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":403400}]}],"group_3":[{"autoTurnFirst":4.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":403400,"motion":100,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_4034_00_04","textHome":"一个人，总会有无法办到的事情。"}]}],"group_30":[{"autoTurnFirst":3.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp.json","id":403400,"motion":1,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_4034_00_38","textHome":"你喜欢绘本吗？原来如此。@我在小的时候也经常看。@绘本是带给了孩子们梦想的存在啊……"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":403400}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.7,"chara":[{"id":403400,"motion":300}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.1,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":1,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":403400}]},{"autoTurnFirst":0.1,"chara":[{"eyeClose":0,"id":403400}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.9,"chara":[{"id":403400}]}],"group_31":[{"autoTurnFirst":7.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":403400,"motion":1,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_4034_00_39","textHome":"成为绘本作家是父亲的梦想，@虽然他的梦想曾经实现了……@但最后，他还是放弃了。@是我让他放弃了梦想……"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"id":403400,"motion":0}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.8,"chara":[{"id":403400,"motion":300}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.0,"chara":[{"eyeClose":1,"id":403400}]}],"group_32":[{"autoTurnFirst":0.1,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":403400,"motion":300,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_4034_00_40","textHome":"我做了对不起父亲的事情，@虽然我一直很后悔……@但亚里纱说的话拯救了我……@我真的很开心。"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.8,"chara":[{"eyeClose":1,"id":403400}]},{"autoTurnFirst":0.1,"chara":[{"eyeClose":0,"id":403400}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.6,"chara":[{"id":403400}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.4,"chara":[{"id":403400,"motion":0}]},{"autoTurnFirst":5.0,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":403400,"motion":1}]}],"group_33":[{"autoTurnFirst":7.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_020.exp.json","id":403400,"motion":1,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_4034_00_41","textHome":"不行。我可不会因为这样的借口就把你放走！@在值日打扫的时候偷懒，@我该怎么让你反省才好呢？哼哼！"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.0,"chara":[{"id":403400,"motion":0}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":403400,"motion":200}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.8,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":403400}]}],"group_34":[{"autoTurnFirst":4.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_020.exp.json","id":403400,"motion":400,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_4034_00_42","textHome":"不管怎么样都放马过来吧！"}]}],"group_35":[{"autoTurnFirst":1.2,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":403400,"motion":100,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_4034_00_43","textHome":"呼，结束了。"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":403400}]}],"group_36":[{"autoTurnFirst":3.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":403400,"motion":200,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_4034_00_44","textHome":"明白就好。"}]}],"group_37":[{"autoTurnFirst":4.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":403400,"motion":100,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_4034_00_45","textHome":"多亏了大家的帮忙！"}]}],"group_38":[{"autoTurnFirst":4.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":403400,"motion":200,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_4034_00_46","textHome":"哎呀，举手之劳。"}]}],"group_39":[{"autoTurnFirst":5.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_020.exp.json","id":403400,"motion":1,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_4034_00_63","textHome":"好好想想应该怎么使用力量吧！"}]}],"group_4":[{"autoTurnFirst":2.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":403400,"motion":0,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_4034_00_05","textHome":"从此以后也……嗯……一定没问题的。"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":1.5,"chara":[{"eyeClose":1,"id":403400}]},{"autoTurnFirst":0.1,"chara":[{"eyeClose":0,"id":403400}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.4,"chara":[{"id":403400,"motion":100}]}],"group_40":[{"autoTurnFirst":3.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_020.exp.json","id":403400,"motion":0,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_4034_00_64","textHome":"放心。"}]}],"group_41":[{"autoTurnFirst":3.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_020.exp.json","id":403400,"motion":400,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_4034_00_65","textHome":"我会让你重新做人的……"}]}],"group_42":[{"autoTurnFirst":4.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":403400,"motion":200,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_4034_00_66","textHome":"看吧，你还是能变乖的吧？"}]}],"group_43":[{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":403400,"motion":0,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_4034_00_02","textHome":"初次见面，我是诗音千里。@嗯，我正在进行风纪的突击检查！@哎呀，你的领带歪了哦。@这样就好了，嗯！"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.2,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"id":403400,"motion":200}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.7,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp.json","id":403400,"motion":400}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.4,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":403400,"motion":1}]}],"group_5":[{"autoTurnFirst":2.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":403400,"motion":1,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_4034_00_13","textHome":"比之前似乎强了一些。@不过，这还远远不够呢！"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":1.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":403400}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":403400,"motion":200}]}],"group_6":[{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp.json","id":403400,"motion":0,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_4034_00_14","textHome":"没想到能走到这一步……@这就是一起加油的成果吧！"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":403400,"motion":200}]}],"group_7":[{"autoTurnFirst":1.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":403400,"motion":1,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_4034_00_15","textHome":"哼哼